class.comment: Represents the status of a stored @({pkg}.MemoryModuleType).

enumerations.name: VALUE_PRESENT
enumerations.comment: The memory is registered, present and has a value.

enumerations.name: VALUE_ABSENT
enumerations.comment: The memory is registered, not present and does not have a value.

enumerations.name: REGISTERED
enumerations.comment: The memory is a valid memory that can be applied to this @(net.minecraft.world.entity.ai.Brain).
